        <text id="2019021313fd5a7bc162430e90000002">
          <inserted>606 <by role="member" id="4841">Mr PICTON (Kaurna)</by> (13 February 2018).  Does the government support calls for aged-care providers to publish their staff to resident ratios?</inserted>
        </text>
      </talker>
      <talker role="member" id="4342" kind="answer">
        <name>The Hon. D.C. VAN HOLST PELLEKAAN</name>
        <house>House of Assembly</house>
